{'Gemini response': "[00:00.000] A wide shot of a fancy hotel lobby. People mill about, waiting to get on an elevator. One of the people waiting is CJ McCollum, an NBA player for the New Orleans Pelicans. He is wearing a black sweatshirt and black pants.\n[00:01.000] The doors to the elevator open and the group begins to enter.\n[00:02.000] Now, CJ McCollum walks onto a basketball court. Several boys, about 10 to 12 years old, are already there. They are wearing white and teal basketball uniforms. The boys' faces light up when they see CJ.\n[00:05.000] The boys sit down on the basketball court, listening intently to instructions. Behind them, CJ McCollum’s red, white, and blue “CJ McCollum All-Star Weekend” logo is visible.\n[00:07.000]  Two of the boys start dribbling basketballs. A coach in a grey t-shirt shows them how to improve their technique.\n[00:09.000]  CJ, now wearing a black Li-Ning sweatshirt, speaks to the boys on the court. He’s with another man wearing a blue sweatshirt with Japanese lettering on it. \n[00:13.000]  CJ, the coach, and the boys put their hands in for a team huddle on the court. They smile and cheer, their excitement building.\n[00:14.000] The boys line up for a photo with CJ and the other coach. They're holding basketballs that have “Li-Ning” and “FIBA Approved” printed on them. \n[00:16.000] Close up on several of the Li-Ning basketballs. In the background, you can see the boys watching CJ perform a basketball drill. \n"}
